title: Hour 2 - Big Ten vs. SEC, Jason Garrett
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Big Ten vs. SEC, Jason Garrett
description:
Dan explains how the Big Ten and SEC are looking to do further battle over media rights through further expansion. NBC NFL Analyst and former NFL HC Jason Garrett stops by to talk about his new job and look back at his stints with the Cowboys and Giants. Plus, Shea in Irving breaks his silence!
